name: minnesota-county-boundaries-1990-census-nad83-version
notes: The LCC GIS Office provides the Legislature with timely, accurate spatial data and is the repository of statewide boundary information for legislative use. The Office was originally set up for 1990 redistricting, and continues to support legislative cartographic needs as well as prepare for 2000 Redistricting. This database of Minnesota county boundaries was developed from U.S. Bureau of the Census 1990 TIGER/Line files as part of the most recent redistricting effort.
